graph TD
    User((User)) -->|1. Query| RL[Redis Sliding Window Rate Limiter]
    RL -->|Allowed| Gateway[Fastify Gateway]
    RL -->|Blocked| 429[Error: 429 Too Many Requests]

    Gateway -->|2. Generate Embedding| Cache{3. Semantic Cache: Redis Stack}
    
    Cache -->|3a. < 0.15 Score Match| Return[Return Response - 11ms]
    Cache -->|3b. Score Miss| Queue[BullMQ Task Queue]
    
    Queue -->|4. Semaphore 1 Control| Worker[Python AI Worker]
    
    Worker --> RAG{5. Mongo Vector Search}
    
    RAG -->|5a. Context Found| Hash{6. Context Hash Check}
    RAG -->|5b. No Context| LLM[7. Groq LLM Inference]
    
    Hash -->|New Hash| Hydrate[Proactive Hydration]
    Hash -->|Existing Hash| LLM
    
    LLM -->|8. Retry Logic/Backoff| Webhook[9. Webhook: /v1/webhook/result]
    
    Webhook -->|10. should_cache=True| Update[Update Redis Cache + Stats]
    Webhook -->|Final Delivery| User

    %% Styles
    classDef user fill:#E3F2FD,stroke:#1E88E5,stroke-width:2px;
    classDef gateway fill:#E8F5E9,stroke:#43A047,stroke-width:2px;
    classDef cache fill:#FFF3E0,stroke:#FB8C00,stroke-width:2px;
    classDef queue fill:#F3E5F5,stroke:#8E24AA,stroke-width:2px;
    classDef worker fill:#E0F7FA,stroke:#00ACC1,stroke-width:2px;
    classDef decision fill:#FCE4EC,stroke:#D81B60,stroke-width:2px;
    classDef llm fill:#EDE7F6,stroke:#5E35B1,stroke-width:2px;
    classDef error fill:#FFEBEE,stroke:#E53935,stroke-width:2px;

    %% Apply classes
    class User user;
    class Gateway,RL,Webhook,Update gateway;
    class Cache cache;
    class Queue queue;
    class Worker,Hydrate worker;
    class Hash,RAG decision;
    class LLM llm;
    class 429 error;
